{"tid":2254392,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得鳩買股票仲衰過賭波？","createTime":"2020-10-22T19:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T23:14:15.000Z","uid":255802,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2825706ec5f63c008b061ce6e16f7410bb3751cd","tid":2254392,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T19:48:17.000Z","msg":"姐係人買tsla 你又跟風買 <br />\n匯豐$30撈底價啊 又真係有傻散信<br />\n當你買一個唔熟悉嘅投資產品嘅時候 <br />\n其實係同賭大細冇分別<br />\n更加唔好提買牛熊連溢價都唔識嗰啲傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但賭波 仲可以參考下往績  <br />\n刷角隊 可以追角大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主攻型球隊 買下大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賤種隊未買佢對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識控制注碼 其實唔難贏錢<br />\n甚至可以當係一個價值投資 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比個數字大家 就係樓豬以前買牛熊針左40k<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買波每個月profit有20-30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108e1b35c678cdd5480ec8ac21ed8bb1a83c7d40","tid":2254392,"uid":71833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T19:48:50.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"28a9e854c14aad73b80e78283fa8215afa3ba16b","tid":2254392,"uid":44044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T19:48:51.000Z","msg":"勁啊169"},{"pid":"bcf56c2e8e06f92f7f15920e443e835cce4c0a5c","tid":2254392,"uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T19:49:51.000Z","msg":"嗱連登仔好簡單嘅啫<br />\n佢冇樓呢就想你地都冇<br />\n佢冇嘅嘢呢就數臭你<br />\n佢有嘅呢就自己吹，例如話自己公屋係人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19035e4923f84bd9ce7f152e4015a0eb6e579e7","tid":2254392,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28a9e854c14aad73b80e78283fa8215afa3ba1